<item>
            <title>[LU-100] Changes made for LU-86 mean that results are not uploaded to Maloo</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-100</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The changes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-86&quot; title=&quot;auster cleanups&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-86&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-86&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mean that the log directory is not passed to the maloo_upload.sh and so logging on or off the results are of testing never logged.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;        if $upload_logs; then&lt;br/&gt;
            $upload_script&lt;br/&gt;
        fi&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should read&lt;br/&gt;
        if $upload_logs; then&lt;br/&gt;
            $upload_script $LOGDIR&lt;br/&gt;
        fi&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
